name: Frank Jenkins Law Office
overview: The Frank Jenkins Law Office was founded by Frank M. Jenkins III to provide legal help to victims of serious personal injury throughout Kentucky.  During our 15 years in practice, our firm has handled cases in a variety of personal injury areas, including vehicle accidents, workers’ compensation, medical malpractice and others.  We have assembled a strong team of professionals to make your experience with the legal system as pleasant and effective as possible.  Our staff will explain every aspect of your case to you, step by step. We want you to feel confident and comfortable about the strategy we pursue on your behalf.
